Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.92,0:00:10.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這東西弄起來還挺棘手的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.24,0:00:14.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因為這樣 才能成為優秀的傀儡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.77,0:00:17.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還在想你到底打算宅多久
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.55,0:00:19.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來在製作新的傀儡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.72,0:00:22.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,組裝超複雜的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.38,0:00:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才沒有宅呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.21,0:00:29.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了備戰嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.92,0:00:36.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.68,0:00:44.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就連木葉都變成了那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.83,0:00:46.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後再發生什麼也不足為奇了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.66,0:00:50.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實 木葉是我們的盟國
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.74,0:00:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法置之度外啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.20,0:00:57.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要重建徹底摧毀的村子可不容易
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.77,0:01:00.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更重要的是填補空缺的火影之位
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.04,0:01:04.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.63,0:01:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是組織上 還是精神上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.07,0:01:10.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身為木葉支柱的火影如今不在了…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.58,0:01:11.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.16,0:01:13.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失手了 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.34,0:01:15.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說實話
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.73,0:01:18.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒了火影 他們能從曉帶來的創傷中重振嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.18,0:01:20.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愛羅
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.51,0:01:24.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.43,0:01:31.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 那裡有他在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.33,0:01:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我不想這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.19,0:01:39.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但對於村子而言 你不過是令人恐懼的兵器
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.37,0:01:44.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今你要離開我們 加入正規部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.65,0:01:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只會徒增痛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.79,0:01:49.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上層都是一些絲毫不顧及你感受的人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.40,0:01:54.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村民大都對你抱有恐懼心理
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.36,0:02:03.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.91,0:02:05.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.35,0:02:08.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可只是空等的話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.75,0:02:11.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更劇烈的痛苦將席捲而至
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.41,0:02:17.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有努力 靠自己解開這個枷鎖了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.67,0:02:21.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕不逃入隻身一人的孤單之路
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.50,0:02:24.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話 終有一天…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.84,0:02:28.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能像那傢伙一樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.34,0:02:34.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和砂隱的共同任務
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.53,0:02:37.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種小事我們去不就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.24,0:02:39.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒那麼簡單
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.71,0:02:42.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是在砂隱和我們的邊境引發的矛盾
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.90,0:02:44.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論委託哪一方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.33,0:02:45.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難免發生口角
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.74,0:02:48.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此 就以同盟國的身份攜手行動
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.47,0:02:51.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是最佳方案嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.55,0:02:53.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最重要的是能輕鬆一些了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.45,0:02:57.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說是同盟國
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.25,0:02:59.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不過是木葉遇襲後結成的同盟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.06,0:03:02.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛開始不可能諸事順利
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.48,0:03:05.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為修復關係的第一步
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.37,0:03:07.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這次任務吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.24,0:03:10.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.08,0:03:11.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真睿智
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.95,0:03:13.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連這些事都明白
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.69,0:03:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.52,0:03:18.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼什麼 到底是怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.35,0:03:20.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這輩子都不會理解的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.77,0:03:24.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是村子間 國家間的大人物們考慮的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.98,0:03:26.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.75,0:03:28.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不至於用這種語氣來說嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.98,0:03:30.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然身為同盟國
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.91,0:03:33.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家融洽相處才好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.36,0:03:38.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 閒談到此結束
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.92,0:03:40.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在要趕往匯合地點了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.21,0:03:43.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 到底誰會最先抵達呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.91,0:03:45.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家比比看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.52,0:03:47.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人 耍賴皮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.58,0:03:52.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一名
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.63,0:03:54.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個小孩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.75,0:03:56.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.71,0:04:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,匯合地點應該就是這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.37,0:04:02.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是來得太早了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.30,0:04:05.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然會遲到 肯定不是什麼好人物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.93,0:04:07.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 一提到砂隱那些傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.91,0:04:09.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道是看不透他們呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.76,0:04:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是他們本來就很奇怪…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.78,0:04:13.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果真心同木葉修好的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.91,0:04:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不應該遲到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.38,0:04:18.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們遲到了 真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.73,0:04:24.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我愛羅
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.24,0:04:29.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偏偏是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.43,0:04:34.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到會和這傢伙一起合作 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.19,0:04:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼 我愛羅 時間剛好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.43,0:04:49.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們只是來早了些
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.33,0:04:51.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.09,0:04:54.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.90,0:04:57.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.14,0:04:59.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來的稍微晚了些
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.75,0:05:01.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.46,0:05:09.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來沒了殺氣 變親和了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.49,0:05:14.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,砂之… 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.93,0:05:16.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對防禦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.78,0:05:21.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛…痛…痛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.31,0:05:23.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 你到底打算幹嗎 鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.48,0:05:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛…痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.84,0:05:26.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是打個招呼而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.10,0:05:28.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扔個石頭什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.38,0:05:31.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能傷到他嘛 對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.12,0:05:34.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那兩位呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.64,0:05:39.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愛羅大人竟然會使出絕對防禦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.66,0:05:41.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是何等恐怖的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.94,0:05:46.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來沒那麼容易被認同嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.17,0:05:48.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 那幫傢伙怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.79,0:05:50.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害怕過頭了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.17,0:05:55.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天京劇王子和鐵扇公主沒一起出動嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.89,0:05:57.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.02,0:05:59.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勘九郎和手鞠才對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.76,0:06:02.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在所屬正規部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.28,0:06:04.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我來介紹一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.72,0:06:07.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我的部下亞歐吉和克羅比
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.54,0:06:08.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是亞歐吉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.04,0:06:10.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是克羅比
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.42,0:06:14.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是這次任務的隊長 旗木卡卡西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.96,0:06:18.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是鳴人 小櫻和佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.16,0:06:19.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.19,0:06:20.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有勞了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.37,0:06:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您好 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.57,0:06:24.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,承蒙關照
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.96,0:06:26.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是些不成熟的部下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.98,0:06:28.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多多關照了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.41,0:06:32.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綜上所述
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.89,0:06:35.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愛羅班從山的西側出發
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.35,0:06:37.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們第七班則從東側出發
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.83,0:06:40.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同時進攻山頂的山賊據點
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.03,0:06:45.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作戰開始時間為子時 行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.76,0:06:51.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說不用等那麼久了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.74,0:06:52.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憑我們幾個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.96,0:06:55.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,區區山賊輕鬆就能搞定啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.42,0:06:58.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說是山賊 他們也是叛忍集團
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.72,0:07:01.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且據說其中也有中忍級別的忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.77,0:07:03.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是 鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.65,0:07:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可別因為你 讓我們幾個都陷入危險啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.78,0:07:10.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.84,0:07:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們明白作戰方案了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.27,0:07:19.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些事想事先打個招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.88,0:07:24.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.16,0:07:25.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我愛羅那傢伙鬼鬼祟祟的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.99,0:07:29.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長們之間也會有需要商討的事嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.30,0:07:35.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙竟然是隊長 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.06,0:07:36.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真臭屁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.90,0:07:40.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有跟蹤者的跡象
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.74,0:07:44.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不出亂子最好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.40,0:07:48.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但總得先跟你們打個招呼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.92,0:07:52.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來你已經有譜了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.32,0:07:57.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被村裡的上層疏遠
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.05,0:08:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許會給你們添麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.60,0:08:04.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正合我意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.14,0:08:09.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木葉和砂隱一起完成任務
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.09,0:08:12.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加深感情 這才是任務的真正意義
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.53,0:08:16.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問題越多羈絆也就越深了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.01,0:08:21.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 鳴人 小櫻 佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.42,0:08:22.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要上路了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.27,0:08:23.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.26,0:08:27.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次可別遲到了 我愛羅
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.66,0:08:32.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.54,0:08:38.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到他會自願加入正規部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.12,0:08:41.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣我們的任務也減輕了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.01,0:08:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.53,0:08:47.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上層們都相當高興吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.42,0:08:50.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來 我們的酬勞也會提高了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.60,0:08:53.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,砂之我愛羅
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.55,0:08:55.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的首級就歸我們了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.71,0:10:47.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說我愛羅大人已經有所改變
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.47,0:10:49.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.53,0:10:55.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,砂之…絕對防禦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.99,0:11:04.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無數忍者命喪於此也是事實
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.32,0:11:10.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是一切順利就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.42,0:11:23.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.38,0:11:24.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是山賊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.70,0:11:25.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.44,0:11:32.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目標是…我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.57,0:11:35.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上層都是一些絲毫不顧及你感受的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.26,0:11:37.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村民大都也對你…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.33,0:11:42.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經決定向前邁進了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.13,0:11:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕不能在這此停留
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.64,0:11:54.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 卡卡西老師
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.23,0:11:56.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底打算跟到什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.37,0:11:58.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我出來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.69,0:12:00.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.89,0:12:06.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是寫輪眼卡卡西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.39,0:12:09.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還以為氣息隱藏得很好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.56,0:12:14.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不用顧忌繼續前進吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.16,0:12:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我並不打算阻撓同盟國的忍者執行任務
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.65,0:12:22.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同盟國
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.55,0:12:24.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,砂隱的人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.90,0:12:29.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將我們視為本次任務的監察者也無妨
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.08,0:12:31.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,監察者…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.84,0:12:33.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是監視者啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.83,0:12:37.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暗地觀察任務的執行情況
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.59,0:12:38.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼監察
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.05,0:12:40.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是卻戴著面具
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.03,0:12:42.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓人信不過
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.13,0:12:43.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.44,0:12:48.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒被信任的恐怕是我愛羅吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.08,0:12:56.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愛羅大人的力量對於我們砂隱…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.87,0:13:01.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 正因為是自家人才更具威脅
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.64,0:13:04.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愛羅大人的術 你們也見識過
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.99,0:13:07.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道你們不覺得嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.08,0:13:10.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是不應該存在的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.76,0:13:16.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們打算除掉我愛羅嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.85,0:13:20.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說 對方還有暗殺部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.95,0:13:25.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對木葉而言不見得是壞事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.30,0:13:29.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為其他村子的一個強大兵器將會消失
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.71,0:13:32.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真過分 竟然將同村裡的忍者給…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.15,0:13:34.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都能明白的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.85,0:13:38.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愛羅大人對於兩方村子來說都是威脅
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.46,0:13:41.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不該存在於世的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.47,0:13:45.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是村子的危險道具
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.65,0:13:49.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對他們而言 是要被抹殺的過去遺物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.55,0:13:53.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時 我是這樣想的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.25,0:13:57.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是不得不這樣想
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.12,0:14:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並且我明白那就是最痛苦的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.70,0:14:05.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這個世界上…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.88,0:14:09.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己就像不被需要的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.98,0:14:14.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我到底為何存在 為何而活呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.47,0:14:18.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愛羅大人絕不能活在這個世上…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.13,0:14:30.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能讓他過去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.48,0:14:34.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使在砂隱 也該有能理解我愛羅的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.56,0:14:38.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們無法接受我愛羅
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.43,0:14:41.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是不理解
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.68,0:14:45.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過可別把我們跟你們混為一談
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.06,0:14:52.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上鉤了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.18,0:15:00.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.04,0:15:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傀儡自己…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.90,0:15:04.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愛羅大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.41,0:15:24.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會被幹掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.88,0:15:26.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.03,0:15:30.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他本就是個毫不在意生命的殺人機器
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.28,0:15:33.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是個只會享受殺戮的怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.30,0:15:36.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愛羅大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.95,0:15:49.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到這麼容易就中計了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.89,0:15:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一來 我們的任務就簡單多了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.45,0:15:59.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傀儡水遁.妖雨之舞 	
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.00,0:16:10.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃出來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.17,0:16:12.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.18,0:16:14.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從哪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.49,0:16:18.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時…我愛羅大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.91,0:16:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.29,0:16:26.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道不是對我們這麼說的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.22,0:16:29.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們平安無事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.53,0:16:31.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愛羅呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.43,0:16:40.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們 怎麼能拋棄同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.99,0:16:46.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.09,0:16:50.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和你…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.73,0:16:53.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有我愛羅大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.32,0:17:04.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,砂子吸收了凝聚查克拉的水 行動變得遲鈍了 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.50,0:17:06.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結合也變弱了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.73,0:17:11.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的忍術已經被封印了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.11,0:17:13.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.76,0:17:15.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.79,0:17:18.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愛羅
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.25,0:17:21.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來救你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.54,0:17:26.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漩渦…鳴人 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.83,0:17:32.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終究只是影分身
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.54,0:17:33.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.48,0:17:34.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真身只有一個
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.93,0:17:36.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不止一個呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.56,0:17:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不會再逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.10,0:17:43.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愛羅大人是我們的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.27,0:17:46.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愛羅大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.52,0:17:48.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扔下您逃走 非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.95,0:17:50.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也要戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.74,0:17:52.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同我愛羅大人一起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.88,0:17:55.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.80,0:18:00.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然被這些廢物給…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.99,0:18:04.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上層真是小看我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.24,0:18:08.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要殺我 戰鬥力還不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.07,0:18:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對付你們這就足夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.31,0:18:29.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盡耍酷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.22,0:18:35.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是災難啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.96,0:18:37.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來我們這邊的那幫人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.66,0:18:39.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基本也被降服了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.16,0:18:43.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你們添麻煩了 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.93,0:18:46.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,添麻煩的是這些傢伙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.79,0:18:47.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.51,0:18:52.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道他們是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.26,0:18:56.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…即便如此
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.56,0:19:00.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們也是砂隱的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.70,0:19:03.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.38,0:19:09.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 繼續我們的任務吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.69,0:19:14.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要從這裡開始嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.72,0:19:18.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從這細微的羈絆之中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.75,0:19:26.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想成為被他人需要的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.88,0:19:34.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是作為讓人畏懼的兵器
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.62,0:19:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是作為砂隱的風影
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.01,0:19:53.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把自己的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.65,0:19:56.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與村裡的同伴們聯繫在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.34,0:19:57.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得到了眾人的認可
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.08,0:20:00.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實現了成為風影的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.61,0:20:03.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是從那傢伙身上學來的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.30,0:20:06.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通過逐漸加深跟同伴的羈絆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.25,0:20:10.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以此找回了原來的自我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.45,0:20:15.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個村子有他的存在 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.71,0:20:20.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比任何人都重視同伴以及同伴間的羈絆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.63,0:20:22.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漩渦鳴人 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.23,0:20:29.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是他和他所珍視的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.66,0:20:31.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次也一定能夠挺過去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.22,0:20:35.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還會變得更加成熟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.45,0:20:54.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說一次…能再說一次剛才你們說的話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.16,0:20:58.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扔下您逃跑 非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.29,0:20:59.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.18,0:21:01.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這句
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.54,0:21:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是之前那句…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.84,0:21:10.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.46,0:22:47.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底在做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.91,0:22:49.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經浪費了這麼多時間
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.54,0:22:51.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒抓到小小的鳴人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.77,0:22:53.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉 綱手大人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.56,0:22:55.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過事態比預想得複雜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.88,0:22:58.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只憑我們醫療班 人手不足啊 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.60,0:23:00.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考慮到之後的損失
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.35,0:23:03.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須得不擇手段嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.48,0:23:05.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 火影忍者疾風傳
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.71,0:23:07.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人 失控
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.43,0:23:10.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人 絕對不會讓你逃掉的
